item.title: CVE-2022-4302|2024-08-03T01:34:50.153Z -- unknown -- white%20label%20cms
item.description: The White Label CMS WordPress plugin before 2.5 unserializes user input provided via the settings, which could allow high-privilege users such as admin to perform PHP Object Injection when a suitable gadget is present.
